name: GetfedonEatStreet
0:
”Alexa, ask food delivery, will Jet's Pizza deliver right now”
”Alexa, open food delivery”
”Alexa, ask food delivery, is Pita Express open”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: food delivery
des:
This skill can check whether a particular EatStreet partner restaurant near you is open. For a delivery related question it can tell you the associated minimum order value and the delivery charges. If the requested restaurant is not found by the skill, it shall provide a few alternative restaurants for you to consider.

Example: For a restaurant named Sam's Cafe, ask, 'Will Sam's Cafe deliver?' OR 'Is Sam's Cafe open now?'

This skill channels data from EatStreet.com. You don't need to have an account on EatStreet to use the skill.

Note: The skill is not developed/managed by EatStreet and is not the official EatStreet.com skill. Your device's address is solely used to check the nearby EatStreet restaurants. See privacy policy at https://eatstreet.esskillboltapps.com/
